## âœ… Summary

NyumbaLink will be a fast, mobile-first platform for connecting tenants with landlords. The MVP emphasizes simplicity: listings, browsing, filtering, and direct calling â€” without any messaging or payment integrations. The app is designed to scale, with a clean tech stack (React, Tailwind, Supabase), and a clear roadmap for future features like maps, messaging, and premium tools.